{"word":"G1432 - δωρεάν - dōreán - do-reh-an' - Without a cause","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δωρεάν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dōreán</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">do-reh-an'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without a cause</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முகாந்தரமில்லாமல், வீணாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"without a cause, freely, for naught, in vain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Accusative case of <a href=\"#/G1431 - δωρεά - dōreá - do-reh-ah'/1431\">G1431</a> as adverb; <i>gratuitously</i> (literally or figuratively): - without a cause, freely, for naught, in vain.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1325/1325\">G1325</a>, <a href=\"#/G1431/1431\">G1431</a>, <a href=\"#/G1432/1432\">G1432</a>, <a href=\"#/G1433/1433\">G1433</a>, <a href=\"#/G1434/1434\">G1434</a>, <a href=\"#/G1435/1435\">G1435</a>, <a href=\"#/G3860/3860\">G3860</a>, <a href=\"#/G3862/3862\">G3862</a>, <a href=\"#/G467/467\">G467</a>, <a href=\"#/G468/468\">G468</a>, <a href=\"#/G469/469\">G469</a>, <a href=\"#/G591/591\">G591</a>"}]}